\tab\cf2\ldblquote No, sir. I\rquote m a sales agent. Any talk we have is not for publication. I \expndtw-1 assure you I am interested in strict privacy.\rdblquote\cf0\expndtw0\par
\tab\cf2\ldblquote Let\rquote s walk down the road a bit. There\rquote s a bench we can use.\rdblquote\cf0\par
\tab\cf2\expndtw-3 We started down. Mrs. Hester walked away. Sally nudged along after us.\cf0\expndtw0\par
\tab\cf2\expndtw-2 I said, \ldblquote You don\rquote t mind if Sally comes along, do you?\rdblquote\cf0\expndtw0\par
