\tab\cf2\expndtw-5 Gellhorn shifted position and his voice got confidential. \i\ldblquote Look \i0 here, Jake, \expndtw-2 let me explain the situation. There\rquote s a big market for private automatics if \expndtw-3 they could only be made cheaply enough. Right?\rdblquote\cf0\expndtw0\par
