\tab\cf2\expndtw-6\ldblquote Well, now, wait a while, Mr. Gellhorn. The motors and bodies aren\rquote t two separate items. They\rquote re a single unit. Those motors are used to their \expndtw-8 own bodies. They wouldn\rquote t be happy in another car.\rdblquote\cf0\expndtw0\par
